    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Style and culture of the African people of the same name living in the Cameroon Grassfields, relatives of the Babanki-Tungo.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
